                <li>Laboratory &amp; diagnostic equipment</li>
                <li>Endoscopy instruments and accessories</li>
                <li>Hospital furniture and fittings</li>
                <li>Rehabilitation and physiotherapy products</li>
                <li>ECG machines, patient monitors, and related devices</li>
