              <p>Yes. Simply add the products you're interested in to your quote list and submit the request form.</p>
              <p>Our sales team will review your requirements and send a tailored quotation, including pricing, lead times, and any applicable bulk discounts — usually within 1–2 business days.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="avm-about-faq__item">
