              <p>Absolutely. We regularly supply hospitals, clinics, and distributors in large quantities.</p>
              <p>Provide us with your bulk order requirements, and we'll offer competitive rates, priority processing, and consolidated shipping to ensure cost-effective delivery.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="avm-about-faq__item">
